data.description: Are you looking for peace, quiet, and the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life? Look no further! Nestled on a one-acre lot, this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a hidden gem located north and east of  McAlester. Step inside to discover a generous living area, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The large windows flood the room with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen has plenty of counter space, modern appliances, and an eat-in dining area with access to the large, covered back patio, perfect to watch the beautiful Oklahoma sunset. Both bedrooms in this home are generously sized, each with its own private bathroom. This layout offers convenience and privacy, making it ideal for families, couples, or guests. Access the large, covered back patio from the kitchen—a serene spot to enjoy your morning coffee or unwind in the evenings. The well-maintained landscaping, peach trees, and firepit in the backyard add to the tranquility and charm of this property. This property is a workshop enthusiast's dream! In 2018, the sellers added a 24x30 workshop with a 12 ft overhead door, providing ample space for DIY projects, storage, or your favorite hobbies. This property offers privacy and serenity and is a haven of peace and seclusion, offering the perfect escape from the daily grind. You'll relish the quiet surroundings and the opportunity to create cherished memories in your own slice of paradise. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a piece of heaven in McAlester.
